<plot>The story of the polygamous families who fled the U.S. in the late 1800's to avoid arrest and imprisonment. The film reveals their overwhelming struggles as they carved out a land of refuge in the desert of northern Mexico only to be driven from their lavish homes and thriving communities by the Mexican revolutionaries a few decades later.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569053</url></doc>
